          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="role">
        <div class="role-meta">
          <span class="label">Designation</span>
          Lead Software Engineer
          <div class="pill-row">
            <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span>6 direct reports</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="role-body">
          <div class="title">Lead Software Engineer</div>
          <div class="dates">Apr 2023 — Dec 2024</div>
          <p class="desc">
            Led six direct reports in delivering microservice architecture and
