            <li><span class="num">04</span><span>Built a <strong>mail-hook service</strong> automating note creation from inbound emails using Azure Event Grid, Graph API, and Service Bus &mdash; eliminating manual data entry on a high-frequency workflow.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <!-- TOUR 2 — SWITCH -->
    <div class="tour">
      <div class="tour-band">
        <div class="idx">Tour 02</div>
        <div class="org">
          <span class="name">Switch, Inc.</span>
          <span class="place">Las Vegas, NV</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dates">Jan 2019 — Apr 2023</div>
      </div>

      <article class="role">
        <div class="role-meta">
          <span class="label">Designation</span>
          Technical Project Manager
        </div>
        <div class="role-body">
          <div class="title">Technical Project Manager</div>
          <div class="dates">Jul 2021 — Apr 2023</div>
          <p class="desc">
            Applied technical expertise to strategic company initiatives under the
            direction of the CTO and EVP of Strategy.
          </p>
          <ul class="actions-list">
